display_name = "Stick"
description = "A small piece of broken timber stripped from the wild. Crude, lightweight, and barely worth noticing, but a survivor knows better than to ignore what the land provides. Useful for simple tools, kindling, or whatever desperate purpose it can be forced to serve."
